Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.94,0:00:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.55,0:00:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你尿完了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.43,0:00:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個傢伙一點都不體貼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.02,0:00:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得為你準備的炸雞塊都快冷掉了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.80,0:00:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！就從最大塊的開始吃起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.87,0:00:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.77,0:01:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 不好意思 是爸爸不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.27,0:01:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得的聖誕節 全部都送給龍之介當禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.70,0:01:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠慷慨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.28,0:01:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.89,0:01:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是貓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.31,0:01:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道是貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.08,0:01:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是問你打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.61,0:01:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好龍之介 不 龍兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.92,0:01:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在是逃亡者 你是知道的是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.17,0:01:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在目前這種情況下很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.10,0:01:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們並沒有多餘的能力再養貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.66,0:01:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介 上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.96,0:01:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捉緊了 別放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.66,0:01:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 貓呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.76,0:01:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下再處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.35,0:02:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.47,0:02:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要全力追趕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.10,0:02:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 我們逃得掉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.18,0:02:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 但是不逃也得逃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.14,0:02:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了後面的小傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.87,0:03:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.08,0:03:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼還不死心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.05,0:03:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在發洩 因為才找不到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.03,0:03:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.27,0:03:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼今日子妳也來試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.59,0:03:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不像妳 有這麼好戰的個性呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.78,0:03:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？那真是太遺憾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常的快樂的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.51,0:03:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶子小姐對不起 他逃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.60,0:04:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請指示下一步該怎麼做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.81,0:04:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.01,0:04:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後還會有很多機會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.44,0:04:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你就先回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.59,0:04:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的主人 現在就回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.75,0:04:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.42,0:04:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你逃到天涯海角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.39,0:04:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定會被我找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.46,0:04:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是意外的聖誕禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.76,0:04:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍兒你沒有問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 龍兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不要讓牠坐車子就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我 都是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.39,0:05:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.89,0:05:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.89,0:05:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試試這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.56,0:05:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.99,0:05:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介！爸爸送給你最珍贵的聖誕禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.93,0:05:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天亮了 起床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.62,0:06:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起床 起床 起床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.87,0:06:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天亮了 天亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.95,0:06:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上了 龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.44,0:06:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起床了 龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.12,0:06:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.97,0:06:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早餐已经準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.75,0:06:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.88,0:06:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 天亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.72,0:06:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會遲到的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.76,0:06:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.85,0:06:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子 對了 就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.73,0:06:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 你快遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.78,0:06:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是 今天要開始上學了是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.24,0:06:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好燙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.59,0:07:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好燙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.52,0:07:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子可不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.98,0:07:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.11,0:07:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來！第一次上學 要鼓足精神出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.15,0:07:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.20,0:07:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.29,0:07:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到學校不是那條路線啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.96,0:07:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.59,0:07:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子 危險 我說危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！電車 電車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.01,0:08:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快停車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.04,0:08:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.50,0:08:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.50,0:08:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心汽車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.55,0:08:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腳踏陣也要小心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.19,0:08:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 一起加油 龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.11,0:08:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是小學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.49,0:08:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能跟溫子一起讀書的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.36,0:08:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是隔壁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.12,0:09:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤井烏小學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.91,0:09:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭！我們不是同一個學校嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.21,0:09:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讓人不安 我不能上那個學校嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.29,0:09:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不行！溫子是高中 要自己一個人讀書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.88,0:09:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.05,0:09:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子的老師是爸爸 所以不要擔心好好加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.23,0:09:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那放學後見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.90,0:09:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.23,0:09:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說老師是父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.07,0:09:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是這樣說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.99,0:09:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那呀...沒有什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.62,0:09:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 要加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.96,0:09:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.60,0:10:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然離開家實在很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.19,0:10:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接到三島會長把機器人實體化的指示的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就悄悄的做了這個決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.53,0:10:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個機器人在性格上 需要在民間使用的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要好幾年的訓練期間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.61,0:10:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你的祖父說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.20,0:10:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就能夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.20,0:10:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說使用的用途只有一種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.04,0:10:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝你提供貴重的研究室 龐大的研究費跟時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.59,0:10:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是絕對不能贊成把它使用在其他的目的上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點請你了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 你到底說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.68,0:10:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是入贅的女婿 真是丟三島家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.39,0:10:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你是想搗亂祖父的用意嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.69,0:10:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太過份了 你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.52,0:10:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有！龍之介的生活教育上暫時由我來照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.32,0:11:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鰥夫能夠到什麼程度 你等著瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.62,0:11:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久作你給我記往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.49,0:11:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久作我不會放過你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.50,0:11:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.92,0:11:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離開家已經有一年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.46,0:11:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是委屈你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.84,0:11:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.51,0:11:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳又在看以前的錄影帶啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.26,0:11:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你管那麼多幹什麼 看什麼是我的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.39,0:11:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊！是沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.65,0:11:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是...阿莉莎錄影的婦女外出服裝秀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莉莎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.61,0:11:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小姐真是很喜歡演藝界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管誰要去離婚也好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.70,0:11:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.45,0:11:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有龍之介少爺的畫面也不要緊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.54,0:11:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.96,0:11:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.63,0:11:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.75,0:11:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個女高中生是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是愛人吧？久作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.88,0:12:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 是你丈夫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.48,0:12:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確是久作的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.23,0:12:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 這不尋常的精力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.36,0:12:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奧林匹克的強化選手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.70,0:12:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.11,0:12:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機器人NK1124
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.03,0:12:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.45,0:12:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已經有了我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.21,0:12:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然還敢要自己喜歡的機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.75,0:12:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而那個女孩子 居然還是個女子高中生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.92,0:12:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.64,0:12:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日子 去跟阿莉莎連絡看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.93,0:12:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個大概是趁龍之介上學的時候拍到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.02,0:12:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在這個附近 一定會有龍之介讀書的小學的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.23,0:13:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去給我查出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.61,0:13:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.78,0:13:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查到了以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.45,0:13:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上給我出動毒氣1號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.41,0:13:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日子趕快去準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.41,0:13:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦連絡上的話就馬上出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.29,0:13:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.37,0:13:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.62,0:13:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有關係！爺爺那一方面我會適時的跟他說明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.46,0:13:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.47,0:13:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你放心 媽媽一定會馬上去救你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.64,0:13:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是那個腳踏車少女出現的大槻信用金庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.81,0:13:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間是早上8點30分左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.94,0:13:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣來想的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.32,0:13:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概這附近可能會有學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.20,0:13:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.82,0:13:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個腳踏車少女是根據電視的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.66,0:13:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是從這個方向來的 也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.45,0:13:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直是由這個方向往這一邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.00,0:14:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.63,0:14:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.17,0:14:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.34,0:14:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.51,0:14:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 預先調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.97,0:14:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想恐怕沒有這個必要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.01,0:14:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒氣1號不是已經下達攻擊命令了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.72,0:14:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要突然闖進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.10,0:14:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有問題啊 如果不在的話怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.98,0:14:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候再說吧 我想應該是沒有問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.06,0:14:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從前我們不都是這麼做的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是只有你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.28,0:14:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說應該算是我的遠親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.95,0:14:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家相處得很好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.50,0:14:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的腳力實在是很驚人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.75,0:14:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼跟那個傢伙會是遠親呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.04,0:14:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有什麼不知道的事情 儘管的問好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.22,0:14:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我當做偶像我是很高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.55,0:14:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣說我的技術很超群 我也很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.89,0:14:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡吃什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.60,0:15:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莢竹魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.98,0:15:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗜好是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.56,0:15:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曬太陽取暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.86,0:15:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在上課中為什麼要做溫子的介紹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.45,0:15:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.32,0:15:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不聽我的課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們太瞧不起人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.08,0:15:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.76,0:15:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不聽你們講什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.13,0:15:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教科書一四六頁翻開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.51,0:15:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.39,0:15:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.94,0:15:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.77,0:15:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏日久作 還有女子高中生機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.36,0:15:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯吧 還是要試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.53,0:15:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是唯一的龍之介少爺都還沒有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.11,0:15:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 阿莉莎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.33,0:16:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要衝進去了 女子高中生機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是毒氣1號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.92,0:16:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.76,0:16:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不舒服是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.76,0:16:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.85,0:16:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.48,0:16:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家我有急事 現在開始自習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.31,0:16:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.32,0:16:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.28,0:16:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.16,0:16:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.95,0:16:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.20,0:16:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子 告訴你在學校要叫我老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.25,0:16:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.77,0:16:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在去把龍之介帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.25,0:16:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙麻煩你對付了要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.45,0:16:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的爸爸...老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.09,0:16:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.80,0:16:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真無聊 上課也聽不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.30,0:17:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又沒什麼事好做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.93,0:17:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連翹課的女孩子也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.02,0:17:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.52,0:17:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們過去看看吧 好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.98,0:17:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮的小姐一塊去喝茶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.82,0:17:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後玩玩遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.45,0:17:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知恥的小子在那兒出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.12,0:17:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他們嚐嚐毒氣彈的威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.71,0:17:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一等 等一等 阿莉莎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的目標是龍之介少爺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.09,0:17:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是為了消除壓力才上機的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.84,0:17:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當0.L.在累積了很多的壓力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.80,0:17:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們哪裡是0.L.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.60,0:17:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社長室直屬遊擊隊 簡稱O.L. 你不知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.39,0:17:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那裡簡稱會是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.60,0:17:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.81,0:17:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管發生什麼事情我都要拚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.07,0:17:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出發 女子高中生機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.40,0:18:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼搞的 到底怎麼搞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.49,0:18:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要開始用功 不要打我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.16,0:18:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚秋鄰家該做什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.29,0:18:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這句話懂的人請舉手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.17,0:18:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.59,0:18:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然搞到這種地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.59,0:18:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.72,0:18:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請放心 這是模擬演習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.60,0:18:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒那麼笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.10,0:18:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓它在街道爆炸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.10,0:18:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要炫耀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.77,0:18:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種情況要怎麼處理呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.98,0:18:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚狀況的是這個機器人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.78,0:18:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上昇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.18,0:19:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.64,0:19:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還用不著發揮毒氣1號的真本領哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.98,0:19:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.07,0:19:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現龍之介少爺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.24,0:19:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快把他帶回來啊 阿莉莎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.55,0:19:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.51,0:19:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.23,0:19:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在三島重工的科學面前 久作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.48,0:20:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是你的科學也沒有辦法匹敵的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.78,0:20:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們期望的靠山也像這樣就斷絕了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.20,0:20:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介少爺趕快一起回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.58,0:20:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶子大小姐...哦 不 是你媽媽正在等你哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.05,0:20:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏日久作你在大小姐面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.42,0:20:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你那個自命不凡的頭 讓你在地面上摩擦摩擦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.90,0:20:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸跟龍之介 絕對都不會讓你給帶走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.95,0:20:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.91,0:20:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個傢伙她也是終結者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.16,0:20:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 夏目溫子是爸爸跟龍之介創作的結晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.48,0:21:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莉莎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.60,0:21:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是做得太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.61,0:21:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是有一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.32,0:21:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.49,0:21:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.29,0:21:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動力鎧甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.33,0:21:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非要讓他好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.75,0:21:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看輕三島重工的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.13,0:21:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被發現要參戰國家的委託
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.50,0:21:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三島重工開發的動力鎧甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.63,0:21:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你一樣都是軍用兵器的新人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.30,0:21:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是兵器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.54,0:22:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.04,0:22:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.34,0:22:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.51,0:22:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莉莎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.76,0:22:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.39,0:22:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去之後告訴晶子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.43,0:22:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不會逃跑的 隨時來找我們好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.48,0:22:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸您太了不起了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.56,0:22:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然了 吃飯去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.63,0:22:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是現在還在上課耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.19,0:22:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐的個性也很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.50,0:22:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么样?毕竟在战斗 還有誰能学习?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.45,0:22:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是夫婦 互不相讓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.16,0:22:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去南西家餐廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.63,0:22:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡吃快餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.49,0:22:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快餐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.21,0:23:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比較喜歡爸爸做的菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.87,0:23:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是碳烤沙丁魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.67,0:23:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就這麼決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.04,0:23:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向晶子問好 再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.30,0:23:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什麼個性嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.05,0:23:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.05,0:23:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很對不起你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.72,0:23:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想毒氣1號有必要改良動力鎧甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.69,0:23:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機械裝置本身不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.06,0:23:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是控制的一方會直接受到衝擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.98,0:23:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守備能力會比較弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.32,0:23:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,體力也無法持久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.61,0:23:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於隨便出動毒氣1號的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.57,0:23:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爺爺很生氣 這怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.83,0:23:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.79,0:23:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是大小姐下達的出動命令嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.46,0:23:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是那個 這個是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.59,0:23:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你們去讓老爺爺教訓一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.30,0:23:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐 太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.47,0:23:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會給你們加發年終獎金的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.80,0:23:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你們繼續看住龍之介他們 拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.18,0:24:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能夠依賴的也只有你們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.94,0:24:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順便給老爺爺訓一訓好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.11,0:24:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.53,0:24:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸謝謝您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.99,0:24:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個也能吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.37,0:24:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈣質是很重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.28,0:24:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吃啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.45,0:24:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,習慣不好 溫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
